                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18151206-159-off878 t18151206-159-cd879"></join>, a great coat, value 1l. a body coat, value 15s. a waistcoat, value 2s. a pair of small-clothes, value 5s. and a knife, value 1s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18151206-159-victim1331" type="victimName">
